FBIS4-68060 "jptot019__l94025" JPRS-TOT-94-019-L JPRS Terrorism FOUO 6 May 1994 NEAR EAST/SOUTH ASIA IRAN Embassy in Athens Denies Links With `17 November' Embassy in Athens Denies Links With `17 November' NC0605175794 Athens ATHENS NEWS in English 6 May 94 p 3 NC0605175794 Athens ATHENS NEWS English BFN [Text] The Iranian embassy in Athens yesterday strongly denied a report in Britain's INDEPENDENT newspaper that Tehran had offered guns to the urban guerrilla groups November 17, of Greece, and the IRA, of Northern Ireland, in exchange for the assassination of Iranian dissidents in Europe. [see previous Terrorism Report] It also rejected allegations it had used drug trafficking money to sponsor international terrorist activities.
